'''飓风艾米莉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Emily}}）是1993年在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]引发创纪录的洪灾，但却自始至终位于海上的一场大型飓风。系统源于8月22日[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]东北方向的一股[[东风波|东风波]]，是这年大西洋飓风季第5场获得命名的风暴和首场飓风。气旋向西北方向移动，于8月25日增强成[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]，然后在[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南方向基本停止移动。之后艾米莉回转西南，但很快又恢复向西北方向前进并增强成飓风。8月31日晚，风暴在逼近北卡罗莱纳州期间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]185公里的最高强度。艾米莉的[[风眼|风眼]]虽有部分从外滩群岛的[[哈特拉斯岛|哈特拉斯岛]]上空经过，但其物理中心距海岸最近时也还有37公里。飓风逐渐减弱，朝东北方向远离海岸，之后又转向东进。此后艾米莉在百慕大东北方向再度止步不前，最终于9月6日在[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南方向洋面消散。

面对风暴威胁，北卡罗莱纳州大部分沿海地区接获[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，警告范围还向北延伸到[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]。[[奥克拉科克岛|奥克拉科克岛]]和哈特拉斯岛实行强制撤离，致使16万人在繁忙的[[劳动节_(美国)|劳动节]]周末流离失所，旅游业收入损失达1000万美元。两岛共有约1600居民在风暴来袭前离开家园，应急官员则留了下来。大部分疏散人员选择前往酒店或亲朋好友家暂避，[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]东南部的商业收入因此大幅提升，当地受到的风暴影响也很小。由于气象机构对艾米莉移动路线的预测结果存在不确定性，弗吉尼亚州、[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]、特拉华州和[[纽约州|纽约州]][[法尔岛|法尔岛]]都有人员疏散。

艾米莉虽然绕过了外滩群岛，但由于此时恰逢月圆，强风与高涨的海潮共同作用，在帕姆利科湾沿线引发严重洪灾。[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]][[巴克斯顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|巴克斯顿]]的水位超过洪水警戒水位达3.21米之多，包括哈特拉斯在内的多个村庄被完全淹没。风暴还刮倒了数以千计的树木，令553套房屋严重受损，其中168套被彻底摧毁，导致哈特拉斯角约四分之一的人口无家可归。整个北卡罗莱纳州受到的结构性破坏估计价值3500万美元。此外，北卡罗莱纳州和弗吉尼亚州海岸沿线共有3名泳客因风暴溺毙。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Emily 1993 track.png}}
飓风艾米莉源于非洲一股于1993年8月17日经过[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]的[[东风波|东风波]]，在穿越大西洋期间逐渐发展，于5天后在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]东北偏东方向约1300公里海域发展出闭合气旋式环流，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将其归类为[[热带低气压|热带低气压]]。低气压向西北方向移动<ref name="prelim01">{{cite report | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081733/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim01.gif | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Emily, 22 August – 06 September 1993 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-09-30 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | page = 1 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，其组织结构在接下来数天内一直都很混乱，环流中心杂乱无章，[[雷暴|雷暴]]时断时续且相对分散，这一定程度上是因为受到北侧[[对流层上层气旋式旋涡|上层低气压]]产生[[风切变|风切变]]的不利影响<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081736/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.002 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.002 | title = Tropical Depression Five Discussion Number 2 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-08-22 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081729/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.004 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.004 | title = Tropical Depression Five Discussion Number 4 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Max | last = Mayfield | date = 1993-08-23 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.007 | title = Tropical Depression Five Discussion Number 7 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Richard | last = Pasch | date = 1993-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003090601/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.007 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月25日，低气压因受逐渐减弱的转向气流影响而基本停止移动<ref name="prelim01" />。随着上层大气环境朝有利于热带气旋发展的方向转变<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081750/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.014 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.014 | title = Tropical Depression Five Discussion Number 14 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first1 = Lixion | last1 = Avila | first2 = Jerry | last2 = Jarrell | date = 1993-08-25 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机发现系统内的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]异常之高，表明气旋已经迅速增强至强烈热带风暴强度，美国国家飓风中心因此将其命名为“艾米莉”（{{lang|en|Emily}}）。次日，该机构根据另一架侦察机测得的每小时120公里风速而把风暴升级成飓风<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | accessdate = 2012-01-17 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 17 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003083151/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.017 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.017 | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-08-26 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] }}</ref>。

成为飓风时，艾米莉的中心位于[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]以东约1600公里海域，并在[[百慕大|百慕大]]以南较远处经过。8月27日，气旋因北侧的[[高压脊|高压脊]]逐渐成形而转向西进。这天，艾米莉的风速在热带风暴和飓风标准间反复波动，但到8月28日又恢复强化趋势，并发展出有利的上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003085542/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.023 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.023 | deadurl = no | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 23 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Lixion | last = Avila | date = 1993-08-28 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref>。气旋行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]较高，在[[气象卫星|卫星图像]]上变得越来越清晰，[[风眼|风眼]]内的[[气压|气压]]也稳步下降<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.024 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Lixion | last = Avila | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081759/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.024 | date = 1993-08-28 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.025 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 25 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Lixion | last = Avila | date = 1993-08-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003091242/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.025 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月29日，前述高压脊的南部边缘被[[短波_(气象学)|短波槽]]侵蚀，艾米莉因此回转向西北方向前进<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.027 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 27 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Lixion | last = Avila | date = 1993-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081742/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.027 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心表示艾米莉的移动路线存在不确定性，[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]和[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]都有可能受到飓风的直接袭击<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.029 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081721/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.029 | date = 1993-08-29 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。随着高气压在北卡罗莱纳州近海再度成形，风暴于8月30日短暂转向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]，然后再开始以长距离弧形路径向北面移动。美国国家飓风中心这时预计艾米莉会保持在海上，但还是有一个[[热带气旋预测模型|热带气旋预测模型]]认为飓风会登岸<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 32 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.032 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003085111/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.032 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Max | last = Mayfield | date = 1993-08-30 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] }}</ref>。

8月31日清晨，侦察机测得的数据表明艾米莉已经达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准，并且由于所在海域水温较高，系统还有可能继续强化<ref>{{cite report | first = Richard | date = 1993-08-31 | last = Pasch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003082245/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.035 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.035 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 35 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。当晚，侦察机又报告风暴已经达到风速每小时185公里，达到[[热带气旋风级|三级飓风标准]]，成为本季首场大型飓风。侦察机还测得时速245公里的飞行高度层风速。艾米莉达到最高强度时，其中心坐落在哈特拉斯岛（{{lang|en|Hatteras Island}}）以东约37公里洋面，并且正在转向北上。风眼直径约为75公里，其中有一部分从哈特拉斯岛和[[帕姆利科湾|帕姆利科湾]]（{{lang|en|Pamlico Sound}}）经过，虽然没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但仍属于直接袭击<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | date = 1993-08-31 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 38 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081719/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.038 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.038 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 }}</ref><ref name="prelim02" />。吹袭外滩群岛后，艾米莉继续沿大规模高气压区边缘移动，转向东北并进入水温较低的海域<ref name="prelim02">{{cite report | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Emily, 22 August – 06 September 1993 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim02.gif | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-09-30 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003085839/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim02.gif | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | page = 2 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.040 | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 40 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 1993-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081715/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.040 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，飓风的风眼仍然非常清晰，风暴强度在9月2日也没有大幅回落<ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 43 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Richard | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.043 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003092100/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.043 | last = Pasch | date = 1993-09-01 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。当晚，气旋受附近的[[低压槽|低压槽]]影响而突然向东大幅转向<ref name="prelim02" />。海域上空的风切变增多，艾米莉因此减弱，眼状特征也迅速消散<ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Emily Discussion Number 45 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003082248/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.045 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.045 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Ed | last = Rappaport | date = 1993-09-02 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] }}</ref>。9月3日，飓风转向东南，并在百慕大东北方向约800公里洋面降级成热带风暴<ref name="prelim02" />，对流这时也已显著恶化<ref name="disc51">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Emily Discussion Number 51 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Max | last = Mayfield | date = 1993-09-04 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003071317/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.051 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.051 | deadurl = no | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 }}</ref>。艾米莉的移动速度再次大幅放缓<ref name="disc51" />，于9月4日晚弱化成热带低气压，只有中心附近还有少量雷暴残存<ref name="prelim02" /><ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081801/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.054 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/tropdisc/nal0593.054 | title = Tropical Depression Emily Discussion Number 54 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Max | last = Mayfield | date = 1993-09-04 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。低气压加速向东北方向移动，于9月6日转变成温带气旋，并且很快就逐渐消散<ref name="prelim02" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:NCOuterBanks-EO.jpg|right]]
美国国家飓风中心对艾米莉的预测基本准确<ref name="prelim03">{{cite report | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929154829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim03.gif | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Emily, 22 August – 06 September 1993 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-09-30 | 9 =  | deadurl = no | format = GIF | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | page = 3 }}</ref>。8月29日，该机构在风暴到达距陆地最近位置两天前向[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[罗曼角国家野生动物保护区|罗曼角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Romain}}）到[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[芬威克岛_(特拉华州)|芬威克岛]]之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，预警范围还包括北卡罗莱纳州的[[阿尔伯马尔湾|阿尔伯马尔湾]]（{{lang|en|Albemarle Sound}}）和帕姆利科湾地区，以及[[帕塔克森特河|帕塔克森特河]]以南的[[切萨皮克湾|切萨皮克湾]]。次日，南卡罗莱纳州[[霍里县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|霍里县]][[利特尔里弗_(南卡罗莱纳州)|利特尔里弗]]（{{lang|en|Little River}}）以南地区的飓风观察预警予以中止。8月30日，[[博格班克斯岛|博格水湾]]到北卡罗莱纳州和[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]边境之间地区接获飓风警告，并于次日延伸至特拉华州[[亨洛彭角|亨洛彭角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Henlopen}}）<ref name="prelim09" />艾米莉转向远离海岸后，所有观察预警和警告均予取消<ref name="prelim09">{{cite report | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Emily, 22 August – 06 September 1993 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-09-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim09.gif | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | at = table 4: Watch and warning summary for Hurricane Emily | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929141117/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim09.gif }}</ref>。

北卡罗莱纳州政府原计划在艾米莉逼近的同一个星期执行为期两天的应急演习，虽然演习也涉及飓风袭击的情况，但风暴来袭仍导致演习推迟<ref>{{cite report | first1 = Dale | last1 = Bechtold | first2 = Joseph | last2 = Pelissier | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003100220/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/rdu06.gif | title = Hurricane Emily in North Carolina: August 28 – September 1, 1993 | year = 1993 | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Releigh, North Carolina) | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/rdu06.gif | at = p. [6]; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | date =  }}</ref>。8月29日，政府建议外滩群岛居民自愿撤离，距气旋来袭还有不到36小时的时候，政府在[[海德县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|海德县]]的奥克拉科克岛（{{lang|en|Ocracoke Island}}）和哈特拉斯岛实行强制撤离<ref name="barnes">{{cite book | first = Jay | last1 = Barnes | pages = 150–153 | title = North Carolina's Hurricane History | date = 2013-06-03 | edition = Fourth | ISBN = 978-1-4696-0652-1 | publisher = University of North Carolina Press | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KjJ1zSk0BoQC&pg=PA150&dq=hurricane+emily+1993&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CEQQ6AEwBWoVChMIuvWF1ur5xwIVTD0-Ch2XQgFM#v=onepage&q=hurricane%20emily%201993&f=false | location = Chapel Hill, North Carolina | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archive-date = 2016-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160624065509/https://books.google.com/books?id=KjJ1zSk0BoQC&pg=PA150&dq=hurricane+emily+1993&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0CEQQ6AEwBWoVChMIuvWF1ur5xwIVTD0-Ch2XQgFM#v=onepage&q=hurricane%20emily%201993&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。共有16万人（其中大部分是游客）从外滩群岛疏散，占当地人口总数的90%<ref name="barnes" />。疏散过程只用了12小时，高速公路巡警令[[158号美国国道|158号美国国道]]和[[莱特纪念大桥|莱特纪念大桥]]（{{lang|en|Wright Memorial Bridge}}）只能朝远离海岸的方向通行，此举令人员撤离的速度大幅提高<ref name="coast">{{cite report | title = Hurricane Emily Assessment: Review of Hurricane Evacuation Studies Utilization and Information Dissemination | docket = 09-716.00 | series = Post-Storm Assessments | date = 1994-06 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archivedate = 2015-10-30 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151030104656/http://coast.noaa.gov/hes/docs/postStorm/H_EMILY_ASSESSMENT_REVIEW_HES_UTILIZATION_INFO_DISSEMINATION.pdf | deadurl = yes | url = http://coast.noaa.gov/hes/docs/postStorm/H_EMILY_ASSESSMENT_REVIEW_HES_UTILIZATION_INFO_DISSEMINATION.pdf }}</ref>。哈特拉斯岛的约1000居民和奥克拉科克岛的约600居民在风暴来袭前离开家园<ref name="barnes" /><ref name="wp91">{{cite news |first=Bill |last=McAllister |title=Hurricane climbs N.C. coast to Virginia |page=A1 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/national/longterm/hurricane/archives/emily93.htm |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]] |date=1993-09-01 |accessdate=2015-11-09 |location=[[哥伦比亚特区|Washington, D.C.]] |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130111122917/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/national/longterm/hurricane/archives/emily93.htm |archivedate=2013-01-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]将人员疏散到大陆，只留下一名骨干成员维护设施<ref name="4b">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 6: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | first = C. Richard | last = Mayson | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003093617/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl04b.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl04b.gif | at = p. 4; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[美国国家公园管理局|美国国家公园管理局]]在风暴来袭两天前就关闭了奥克拉科克岛上的露营地<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1993-08-30 | title = Emily keeps Carolina coastal towns guessing | first1 = Heather | last1 = Dewar | first2 = Martin | last2 = Merzer | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | page = 4A | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/mh0830p5.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003122510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/mh0830p5.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref>。北卡罗莱纳州东南部也有多个城镇疏散，整个区域的许多学校关闭<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Weather Service  Forecast Office (Wilmington, Delaware) | title = Post-Storm Hurricane Report | date = 1993-09-01 | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003101310/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/ilm.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/ilm.gif | accessdate = 2015-09-13 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

由于气象机构的预测结果存在不确定性，艾米莉有转向东北的可能，[[弗吉尼亚州州长|弗吉尼亚州州长]][[道格拉斯·怀尔德|道格拉斯·怀尔德]]（{{lang|en|Douglas Wilder}}）宣布全州进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，并下令[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]待命<ref name="rt91">{{cite news | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0901p2.gif | title = Hurricane's edge batters Outer Banks | date = 1993-09-01 | newspaper = Richmond Times-Dispatch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003120249/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0901p2.gif | location = Richmond, Virginia | page = A1 | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[弗吉尼亚海滩|弗吉尼亚海滩]]官员建议住在海滨及低洼地区的居民疏散<ref name="norfolk" />，位于切萨皮克湾的[[阿可麦克县_(弗吉尼亚州)|阿可麦克县]][[丹吉尔岛|丹吉尔岛]]（{{lang|en|Tangier Island}}）发布强制撤离令。政府还建议住在移动房屋或正在露营的居民前去避难所<ref name="rt91" />。弗吉尼亚州至少有750人离开家园，其中711人住进风暴避难所。[[诺福克国际机场|诺福克国际机场]]关闭了13小时<ref name="norfolk">{{cite report | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Norfolk, Virginia) | title = Post-Storm Report Hurricane Emily | date = 1993-09-10 | accessdate = 2015-09-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/orf01.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003095455/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/orf01.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>，铁路运输也予暂停<ref>{{cite news | first = Peter | last = Bacqué | newspaper = Richmond Times-Dispatch | date = 1993-09-01 | title = Virginia usually spared – North Carolina absorbs brunt of hurricanes | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003100955/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0901p6.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0901p6.gif | location = Richmond, Virginia | page = A13 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>。北面[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[大洋城_(马里兰州)|大洋城]]官员在气旋逼近前宣布进入一级警戒状态，并建议游客离境。马里兰州海岸有约10万人撤离，3600人躲进风暴避难所<ref>{{cite report | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Baltimore, Maryland) | title = Post-Storm Report Hurricane Emily | date = 1993-09-02 | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929122207/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/bwi.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/bwi.gif | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。特拉华州有892人在自愿撤离后躲进风暴避难所<ref>{{cite report | first = Kirk | last = Lombardy | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Wilmington, Delaware) | title = Preliminary Storm Report: Hurricane Emily | date = 1993-09-02 | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/ilg.gif | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003112445/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/ilg.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>。[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]多个海滩因大浪的威胁而关闭<ref name="ap92">{{cite news |first=F. Allen |last=Boyce |date=1993-09-02 |title=Emily leaves damage on Outer Banks, relief elsewhere |agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |newspaper=Northern Star |location=DeKalb, Illinois |accessdate=2015-11-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151109122346/http://northernstar.info/city/emily-leaves-damage-on-outer-banks-relief-elsewhere/article_fa133ad3-0e87-5857-a7af-0ac533a03d2c.html |archivedate=2015-11-09 |url=http://northernstar.info/city/emily-leaves-damage-on-outer-banks-relief-elsewhere/article_fa133ad3-0e87-5857-a7af-0ac533a03d2c.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。纽约州[[法尔岛|法尔岛]]（{{lang|en|Fire Island}}）有约2万人疏散<ref name="prelim03" />。美国大西洋海岸面对艾米莉的威胁共开设了33个应紧避难所<ref name="7b">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 6: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003105800/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl07b.gif | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = C. Richard | last = Mayson | at = p. 7; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl07b.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>，不过，大部分撤离人员还是选择前往酒店或亲朋好友家躲避<ref name="coast" />。

[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]对飓风的防灾准备工作提供协调和帮助。[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]将此前已在[[1993年美国大洪水|1993年美国大洪水]]期间使用的发电设备送到位于北卡罗莱纳州的[[布拉格堡_(北卡羅來納州)|布拉格堡]]（{{lang|en|Fort Bragg}}）<ref name="6b">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 6: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = C. Richard | last = Mayson | at = p. 6; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003123944/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl06b.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl06b.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref>，[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]则在风暴可能袭击的地区储存食品。外滩群岛的电力公司切断供电，降低设施受损和人员触电的风险<ref name="9b">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 6 Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = C. Richard | last = Mayson | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl09b.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003111659/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/fatl09b.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | at = p. 9; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>。[[诺福克海军基地|诺福克海军基地]]有28艘舰船开到海上避开风暴，飞机也撤至别处，非必要人员回家待命<ref name="wp91" /><ref name="norfolk" />。北卡罗莱纳州政府在艾米莉来袭前宣布不会设立州救灾基金，而是依靠包括[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]和[[救世军|救世军]]这样的民间救济组织<ref name="4b" />。美国国家公园管理局预先安排60名工作人员准备电锯，帮助清理倒落的树木<ref name="6b" />。飓风来袭时正逢繁忙的[[劳动节_(美国)|劳动节]]周末，旅游业因此遭受了约1000万美元的业务损失<ref name="erh">{{cite report |publisher=National Weather Service Forecast Office (Newport/Morehead City, North Carolina) |title=Hurricane Emily – August 31, 1993 |first=Chris |last=Collins |date=2011-10-18 |accessdate=2015-09-14 |url=http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/EventReviews/19930831/19930831.php |series=Event Summaries/Case Studies |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203063121/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/mhx/EventReviews/19930831/19930831.php |archivedate=2013-12-03 }}</ref>。不过，许多疏散人员待在弗吉尼亚州东南部，令当地周末的商业收入大幅增加<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Richmond Times-Dispatch | date = 1993-09-02 | first = Andrew | last = Petrofsky | first2 = Wes | last2 = Allison | title = Storm's impact on Va. tourism good and bad | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003122733/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0902p4.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0902p4.gif | format = GIF | location = Richmond, Virginia | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

