=== 北卡罗莱纳州 ===
艾米莉逼近北卡罗莱纳州外滩群岛期间，位于哈特拉斯角近海的[[钻石浅滩灯塔|钻石浅滩灯塔]]（{{lang|en|Diamond Shoal Light}}）测得每小时159公里的2分钟持续风速，阵风时速则达到237公里。距海岸更近的帕姆利科湾地面风速达到每小时185公里。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]巴克斯顿（{{lang|en|Buxton}}）办事处测得的持续风速为每小时96公里<ref name="prelim02" />，阵风时速则达到158公里，之后风速测量仪器因有水灌入而失效，所以实际数值可能更高。位于某商业大楼的风速测量站测得时速172公里的阵风，这一数据虽然可靠，但不属于官方纪录<ref name="twenty">{{cite news | first = Irene | last = Nolan | title = Remembering Hurricane Emily: It was the 'hurricane of the century' | date = 1993-10 | newspaper = Island Free Press | location = Frisco, North Carolina}} archived in {{cite report | title = Hurricane Emily, August 31, 1993 – 20th Anniversary | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Newport/Morehead City, North Carolina) | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | date = n.d. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930194826/http://www.weather.gov/mhx/Emily | archivedate = 2015-09-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.weather.gov/mhx/Emily }}</ref><ref name="water">{{cite book | title = Summary of Floods in the United States, January 1992 Through September 1993 | year = 1993 | editor-first1 = C.A. | editor-last1 = Perry | editor-first2 = L.J. | editor-last2 = Combs | url = http://pubs.usgs.gov/wsp/2499/report.pdf | chapter = Summary of Floods of 1993: August 31, 1993, Storm Surge and the Flood of Hurricane Emily on Hatteras Island, North Carolina | publisher = United States Geological Survey | location = Reston, Virginia | series = Water Supply Paper | first1 = J. Curtis | last1 = Weaver | first2 = Thomas J. Jr. | last2 = Zembrzuski | archivedate = 2015-10-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004135559/http://pubs.usgs.gov/wsp/2499/report.pdf | format = PDF | chapter-url = http://ks.water.usgs.gov/pubs/reports/wsp.2499.sumnc0893.html | number = 2499 | accessdate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref>。飓风在此期间的移动速度较为缓慢，所以上述狂风持续了好几个小时<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Richmond Times-Dispatch | date = 1993-09-02 | first = Bill | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929124049/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0902p1.gif | last = Geroux | title = 'It was unbelievable here': Hurricane leaves much of Hatteras Island in shambles | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/rt0902p1.gif | location = Richmond, Virginia | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。外滩群岛还可能出现两场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]<ref name="hat" />。哈特拉斯岛南侧正逢涨潮<ref name="prelim02" />，风暴袭击期间，巴克斯顿出现高达3.1米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="prelim03" />。大浪引发中等程度的海滩侵蚀，程度可与冬季风暴相提并论<ref name="hat">{{cite report | first = James | last = Ireland | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Cape Hatteras, North Carolina) | date = 1993-09-02 | title = Preliminary Storm Report: Hurricane Emily | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929192624/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat.gif | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | format = GIF | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>。艾米莉在外滩群岛产生的降雨量也比较多，其中又以巴克斯顿最高，有191毫米<ref name="rain">{{cite book | at = section [http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/emily1993.html "Hurricane Emily – August 31 – September 1, 1993"] | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | date = 2013-03-06 | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | first = David M. | last = Roth | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907091138/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | archivedate = 2015-09-07 }}</ref>。更为内陆的地区降雨量很小，[[蒂勒尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|蒂勒尔县]]冈姆内克（{{lang|en|Gum Neck}}）测得的雨量仅有25毫米<ref name="srcc02">{{cite report | publisher = Southeast Region Climate Center | title = Special Climate Summary: Hurricane Emily | date = 1993-08 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003110213/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/srcc02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/srcc02.gif | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | format = GIF | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

气旋造成的总体破坏程度不及预期<ref>{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga01.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003213959/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga01.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF | at = p. 1; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>，破坏范围基本局限在戴尔县和海德县的多个屏障岛<ref name="fem6">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003214616/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga06.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga06.gif | at = p. [6]; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>。哈特拉斯岛有27公里范围区域受到风暴引发的严重洪灾影响<ref name="ncdc">{{cite journal |page=94 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bWJundte?url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-2D90CC02-E4F0-4B19-80D3-54296FF9B9F6.pdf |journal=Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena |archivedate=2015-09-13 |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS-9612DD49-0CBE-4970-A932-1896A778A4CE.pdf |title=New York, Coastal Cont'd: Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena |volume=35 |issue=8 |last=Goodge |first=Grant |date=1993-08 |issn=0039-1972 |deadurl=yes |format=PDF |access-date=2015-11-10 }}</ref>。艾米莉来袭时适逢满月引发强烈[[潮汐|潮汐]]<ref name="barnes" />，狂风令帕姆利科湾的水流南下，大陆海岸水平面下降的同时，有多个屏障岛被淹<ref name="wp91" />，相比之下，这些岛靠海一面出现的潮汐洪灾则非常轻微<ref name="hat2">{{cite report | first = James C. | last = Ireland | title = Hurricane Emily Post Storm Report | date = 1993-09-13 | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Cape Hatteras, North Carolina) | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat02.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003213354/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat02.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>。[[弗里斯科_(北卡罗莱纳州)|弗里斯科]]（{{lang|en|Frisco}}）和[[哈特拉斯_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯]]沿帕姆利科湾的水位比正常水平要高出2.6米，超过8年前[[飓风格洛丽亚|飓风格洛丽亚]]所创纪录<ref name="wp91" /><ref name="ncdc" />，有可能是[[1899年圣奇里亚科飓风|1899年圣奇里亚科飓风]]后当地出现的最高水位。巴克斯顿的水位上涨速度一度达到每小时0.9到1米，超出洪水警戒水位达3.21米之多，包括哈特拉斯在内的多个村庄被完全淹没。[[哈特拉斯角国家海岸|哈特拉斯角国家海岸]]沿线只有最高的沙丘仍然保持干燥，巴克斯顿以北的部分沙丘地段几乎被水冲走<ref name="water" />。洪灾比预测的百年一遇程度还要高0.3至0.6米，冲破许多窗户并灌入房屋<ref name="erh" />，一些还留在家中的居民只能经阁楼逃离<ref name="ncdc" />，戴尔县紧急行动中心的官员也因洪水入侵被迫撤离<ref name="barnes" />。美国国家气象局驻哈特拉斯角办事处被淹，这在该办事处自1957年设立以来还是破天荒的头一遭<ref name="hat2" />，其中的雨量图表和天线都受到持续性的破坏<ref name="hat5">{{cite report | first = James | last = Ireland | title = Hurricane Emily Post Storm Report | date = 1993-09-13 | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Cape Hatteras, North Carolina) | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003213957/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat05.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/hat05.gif | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。许多停在[[游船码头|游船码头]]的船只沉没<ref name="srcc02" />，数百辆停在街头及停车场的汽车被洪水带走，被淹的警车因线路受损而不断发出警笛<ref name="hat2" />。更偏北面的地区中基本上只有奥克拉科克岛受到风暴影响<ref>{{cite news | first = Peter | last = Applebome | date = 1993-09-02 | title = Hurricane Emily: Near miss revives debate over building on islands | newspaper = [[纽约时报|New York Times]] | accessdate = 2015-09-17 | archivedate = 2015-10-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151011191655/http://www.nytimes.com/1993/09/02/us/hurricane-emily-near-miss-revives-debate-over-building-on-islands.html | location = New York, New York | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1993/09/02/us/hurricane-emily-near-miss-revives-debate-over-building-on-islands.html }}</ref>。

艾米莉产生的狂风摧毁了许多屋顶，还刮倒了数以千计的树木，令大量输电线缆中断，还有很多广告牌和屋棚受损<ref name="barnes" /><ref name="hat2" /><ref name="fem11">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga11.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003223136/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga11.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | at = p. 11; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] }}</ref>。位于[[俄勒冈水湾|邦纳大桥]]（{{lang|en|Bonner Bridge}}）以南的城镇全部停电<ref name="fem7" />，至少有1500人受影响<ref name="mh92">{{cite news | location = Miami, Florida | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1993-09-02 | first = Martin | last = Merzer | first2 = Phil | last2 = Long | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | title = Cape Hatteras homes, roads washed away | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/mh0902p4.gif | page = 26A | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003222112/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/news/mh0902p4.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-03 }}</ref>，巴克斯顿也在主管线受损后失去供水<ref name="fem7">{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | at = p. 7; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081738/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga07.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga07.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>。

狂风和洪水的共同摧残导致外滩群岛有553套民宅无法居住<ref name="ncdc" />，其中168套完全被毁<ref name="twenty" />，3套被水冲走<ref name="fem11" />，被毁的房屋中有6套是海岸警卫队所有<ref name="fem6" />。受损最严重的房屋大部分都是老旧的民房，或是没有达到[[建筑规范|规范要求]]的建筑<ref name="barnes" />。哈特拉斯有约25%的居民流离失所<ref name="erh" />。哈特拉斯角学校遭受了价值约310万美元损失<ref name="water" />，1.2米深的洪水摧毁了学校的许多计算机和教科书<ref name="barnes" />。[[北卡罗莱纳州12号高速公路|12号高速公路]]因潮汐洪灾、沙子和瓦砾的共同影响被迫封闭，道路沿线的交通信号灯受损<ref name="4b" />，有两截路段被倒塌的树木阻塞<ref name="wp91" />。路上还出现多个[[沉洞|沉洞]]，其中部分有3辆汽车大小<ref name="erh" />。估计整个北卡罗莱纳州共因这场风暴遭受了价值3500万美元的破坏，其中大部分都发生在哈特拉斯岛<ref name="prelim03" />，并以亚冯村以南情况严重<ref name="ncdc" />。戴尔县小镇[[纳格斯黑德_(北卡罗莱纳州)|纳格斯黑德]]（{{lang|en|Nags Head}}）有两人前往已经关闭的海滩游泳，最终因遭遇大浪丧生<ref name="prelim03" /><ref name="rdu01">{{cite report | first1 = Dale | last1 = Bechtold | first2 = Joseph | last2 = Pelissier | title = Hurricane Emily in North Carolina: August 28 – September 1, 1993 | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Raleigh, North Carolina ) | date = 1993 | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | at = p. 1; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003220635/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/rdu01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/rdu01.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>，还有1人在从洪水淹没的家中逃出时受伤<ref name="ncdc" />。

=== 其它地区 ===
飓风艾米莉对北卡罗莱纳州以外地区造成的影响较小，[[切萨皮克湾隧桥|切萨皮克湾隧桥]]的阵风时速约为59公里<ref name="prelim07">{{cite report | at = table 2: Hurricane Emily selected surface observations | publisher = National Hurricane Center | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Emily, 22 August – 06 September 1993 | first = Miles | last = Lawrence | date = 1993-09-30 | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/ Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily, 1993] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim07.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929134852/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/prenhc/prelim07.gif | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。位于风暴北面的马里兰州大洋城测得71毫米降水<ref name="prelim03" />。向南远至南卡罗莱纳州的[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]都测得高于正常水平的潮汐<ref>{{cite report | first = Richard | last = Shenot | date = 1993-09-08 | title = Preliminary Storm Report: Hurricane Emily | publisher = National Weather Service Forecast Office (Charleston, South Carolina) | accessdate = 2015-09-13 | archivedate = 2015-09-29 | deadurl = no | at = archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929122207/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/bwi.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/bwi.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>，更北面地区的潮汐也有上涨，切萨皮克湾隧桥和特拉华州[[刘易斯_(特拉华州)|刘易斯]]的风暴潮分别有0.37和0.18米高<ref name="prelim07" />。大浪致使弗吉尼亚州海岸出现海滩侵蚀<ref name="srcc02" />，弗吉尼亚海滩的[[桑布里奇_(弗吉尼亚海滩)|桑布里奇]]（{{lang|en|Sandbridge}}）沿海地区因海浪引发轻度洪灾<ref name="norfolk" />，当地1名泳客因强烈的拍岸浪和暗流溺亡<ref name="ncdc" />。艾米莉引发州内多地停电，[[汉普顿锚地隧桥|汉普顿锚地隧桥]]和约5000位市民受到影响。[[纽波特纽斯|纽波特纽斯]]的里霍尔（{{lang|en|Lee Hall}}）有一幢房屋的屋顶因[[闪电|闪电]]起火。弗吉尼亚州此时正遭受持久的旱期影响，飓风产生的少量降水还不足以大幅缓解旱情<ref>{{cite news | title = Emily leaves nasty reminder: Storm knocks out power, causes fire | first = Matt | last = Murray | newspaper = Daily Press | location = Newport News, Virginia | date = 1993-09-02 | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | url = http://articles.dailypress.com/1993-09-02/news/9309020048_1_virginia-power-rains-lightning | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003070759/http://articles.dailypress.com/1993-09-02/news/9309020048_1_virginia-power-rains-lightning }}</ref>。此外，纽约州法尔岛也因恶劣海况和高涨的海潮引起沿海洪灾<ref name="ncdc" />。

== 善后 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Emily_radar_image.gif|thumb]]
艾米莉产生的陆上风速减缓后，多个评估组前去评估飓风产生的破坏程度<ref>{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003085539/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga03.gif | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | at = p. 3; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga03.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>。联邦紧急事务管理局将风暴对北卡罗莱纳州选民的威胁告知该州国会议员<ref>{{cite report | title = Situation Report (SITREP) No. 7: Hurricane Emily | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 1993-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003091630/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga05.gif | accessdate = 2015-11-10 | first = Glenn C. | last = Woodard | at = p. 5; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femaga05.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>，该机构之后因在防灾准备工作上的及时应对赢得赞誉<ref name="idia">{{cite conference | conference = Rutgers Model Congress 2007 | date = 2007-04 | publisher = Institute for Domestic and International Affairs | first = Jessica | last = Fliegelman | title = FEMA Reform | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | pages = 6–9 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004101341/http://www.idia.net/Files/ConferenceCommitteeTopicFiles/62/PDFFile/C07-SHS-FEMAReform.pdf | location = East Brunswick, New Jersey | archivedate = 2015-10-04 | format = PDF | url = http://www.idia.net/Files/ConferenceCommitteeTopicFiles/62/PDFFile/C07-SHS-FEMAReform.pdf }}</ref>。9月1日，外滩群岛的所有机场都已重新开放<ref name="fem6" />。面对大范围地区的停电情况，供电公司派直升机前往相应地区评估损失<ref>{{cite report | first1 = James B. | last1 = Hunt | first2 = Thurman B. | last2 = Hampton | title = Situation Report #12 | publisher = North Carolina Department of Crime Control and Public Safety's Division of Emergency Management | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | at = p. 1; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003091627/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femanc01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femanc01.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。预计停电情况会持续两个星期<ref name="fem7" />。另外，有6辆应紧车辆被派往戴尔县提供饮用水<ref>{{cite report | first1 = James B. | last1 = Hunt | first2 = Thurman B. | last2 = Hampton | title = Situation Report #12 | publisher = North Carolina Department of Crime Control and Public Safety's Division of Emergency Management | date = 1993-09-01 | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femanc02.gif | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | at = p. [2]; archived by the National Hurricane Center in its [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily Storm Wallet for Hurricane Emily] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003081723/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/emily/preloc/femanc02.gif }}</ref>。

9月3日，[[北卡罗莱纳州州长|北卡罗莱纳州州长]][[吉姆·亨特|吉姆·亨特]]（{{lang|en|Jim Hunt}}）宣告该州为灾区<ref name="water" />，时任[[美国总统|总统]][[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]则在1周后宣告戴尔县为联邦灾区，当地居民因此可以申请联邦援助，地方政府也可以在重建公共建筑方面请求[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]援助<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Association | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | title = Designated Areas: North Carolina Hurricane Emily | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003072018/https://www.fema.gov/disaster/1003/designated-areas | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | url = https://www.fema.gov/disaster/1003/designated-areas | year = 1993 | number = DR-1003 | date =  }}</ref>。联邦紧急事务管理局向亚冯（{{lang|en|Avon}}）的444人提供了约100万美元住房援助金，还批准153笔申请提供了约40万美元个人补助。[[小型企业管理局|小型企业管理局]]一共收到812笔小型企业贷款申请<ref>{{cite journal | journal = Coastal Review | publisher = North Carolina Coastal Federation | volume = 12 | issue = 4 | year = 1993 | title = Hurricane Emily: A Reminder of our Vulnerability | page = 6 | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003142829/http://library.uncw.edu/web/collections/manuscript/MS313/CoastalReviews/11041993.pdf | url = http://library.uncw.edu/web/collections/manuscript/MS313/CoastalReviews/11041993.pdf }}</ref>。

9月1日，多个避难所已经关闭，居民相继返回家园，不过哈特拉斯岛在接下来几天里仍然没有向公众开放，只允许应急工作人员进出<ref name="fem7" />。哈特拉斯多个地方企业受到打击，当地失业率因此上扬<ref name="twenty" />，许多餐馆因冰箱在风暴期间失去供电导致食品变质<ref name="srcc02" />。居民家中因风暴破坏产生的各种垃圾堆放在公路上，这其中又以12号高速公路情况突出，工作人员随即进行清理<ref name="twenty" />。这条高速公路经过抢修很快就恢复通行，修复成本约有100万美元<ref>{{cite web | title = Copy of NC 12 Storm Repair Costs | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151003033606/http://www.wral.com/asset/news/local/wral_investigates/2012/11/19/11793749/1353363530-Copy_of_NC_12_Storm_Repair_Costs_2_.pdf | publisher = WRAL-TV | work = WRAL Investigates | url = http://www.wral.com/asset/news/local/wral_investigates/2012/11/19/11793749/1353363530-Copy_of_NC_12_Storm_Repair_Costs_2_.pdf | date = 2012-11-19 | type = Cost table | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | archivedate = 2015-10-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。艾米莉过后不到两周，许多企业已恢复运营，清理工作已经展开，哈特拉斯岛重新向游客开放<ref name="twenty" />。当地的清理作业持续时间从数周到数月不等<ref name="barnes" />。飓风过去3个月后，哈特拉斯角供水中的含[[氯|氯]]量因海水侵入而从原本的每升40毫克上升到280毫克，又过了3个月才恢复之前浓度<ref name="water" />。约50位屋主已经重新建好足以抵御将来类似灾害的房屋，所花费的资金部分来自洪灾保险赔偿金<ref>{{cite journal | title = Flood Retrofit of Coastal Residential Structures: Outer Banks, North Carolina. | journal = Journal of Water Resources Planning and Management | first1 = Paul A. | last1 = Work | first2 = Spencer M. Jr. | last2 = Rogers | first3 = Robert | last3 = Osborne | volume = 125 | issue = 2 | page = 88–93 | date = 1999-03-01 | accessdate = 2016-03-24 | url = http://ascelibrary.org/doi/abs/10.1061/%28ASCE%290733-9496%281999%29125%3A2%2888%29?journalCode=jwrmd5& | doi = 10.1061/(ASCE)0733-9496(1999)125:2(88)}}</ref>。

